{"tid":1917100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"最近啲前線，係咪好似越嚟越細個？","createTime":"2020-03-09T09:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T14:50:33.000Z","uid":211994,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"945d2d6894da64279d2323e429155714ae0fcc02","tid":1917100,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"利申我唔係前線，唔清楚係咪實際情況<br />\n但留意到最近大部分被捕手足都係大約13-16歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪因為<span style=\"color: red;\">大個啲個班已經比狗咬哂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人員高度流失會造成新手冇辦法儲經驗同埋學習<br />\n增加佢地比狗咬嘅危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢度有一篇整合出嚟嘅前線指南/教學<br />\n希望可以幫到咁多位新手老手前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你覺得有咩內容可以加落去呢篇整合度都可以話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算依家係抗疫期間，前線手足都一樣咁忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e97a937488422689f70b7313f652e17e2e7859b","tid":1917100,"uid":211994,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"其實要班咁細個嘅手足學呢啲野已經好病態<br />\n希望多啲有能力嘅人勇敢啲同佢地並肩作戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4960a73014306c75fb652a0f6299e6d9144d84bb","tid":1917100,"uid":67332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"係呀屌"},{"pid":"8189b05b938d3f1ae0cea3aae2055bf6ee6b3ca9","tid":1917100,"uid":49329,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:01:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得係班死黑警專拉細路，令所有家長唔敢俾佢哋出嚟就真。"},{"pid":"2084352699d657aaed211f4bd62de3a95b980956","tid":1917100,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"265dd595989b571e622e9d